<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Blood Donation Eligibility Notification</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: '#E53935', // Red from your palette
                        secondary: '#1E88E5', // Blue from your palette
                        accent: '#F5F5F5', // Light Grey from your palette
                        dark: '#212121', // Black from your palette
                        bgdark: '#1e1e1e', // dark background
                    },
                },
            },
        };
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-accent font-sans text-dark">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto bg-white p-6 rounded shadow-md">
        <div class="bg-bgdark text-white p-8 text-center">
            <img
                src="logo.png"
                alt="BloodBridge Logo"
                class="mx-auto h-24"
            />
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Blood Donation Eligibility Notification</h1>
            <p class="mb-4">Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p class="mb-4">Thank you for your interest in donating blood through BloodBridge.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">We regret to inform you that based on the information provided, you do not meet the eligibility criteria for blood donation at this time.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">The specific reasons for ineligibility are as follows:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                <li>Minimum Age Requirement: You must be at least 18 years old to donate blood.</li>
                <li>Minimum Weight Requirement: You must weigh at least 52kg to donate blood.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-300 my-4"></div>
            <p class="mb-2">According to the details you provided:</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Age:</strong> <%= age %> years</p>
            <p class="mb-4"><strong>Weight:</strong> <%= weight %> kg</p>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-300 my-4"></div>
            <p class="mb-4">We encourage you to meet these requirements and reapply in the future. Your willingness to donate is greatly appreciated, and we hope to welcome you as a donor once you meet the eligibility criteria.</p>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Note:</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">If you believe there has been an error or if you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@bloodbridge.com" class="text-secondary hover:underline">support@bloodbridge.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bgdark text-primary p-4 text-center">
            <p class="mb-2">Thank you for your understanding and support.</p>
            <p>Sincerely, <br />The BloodBridge Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>